#We Scare Hunger!

##When: October 20- November 11
##What: Non-Perishable food items- No Glass! (canned meals, canned foot/vegetables, soy sauce bottles, spices)
##Why: Millions of people go hungry every single day. Believe it or not, some of these people are even in our own backyard. By bringing in canned goods for our peers, you can help in the process of eliminating poverty!
##Who: All students at Miller

##For every two cans of food brought to the Fright Night Dance, you will receive one free soda(while supplies last)!
##Encourage classmates to go trick-or-treating for canned goods on Halloween!
